ef=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerover_event\"><code>pointerover</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\"><code>readystatechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>document.designMode</code> controla se&nbsp;o documento todo&nbsp;é editável. Valores validos são&nbsp;<code>\"on\"</code>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<code>\"off\"</code>. De acordo com a especificação, esta propriedade é por padrão&nbsp;<code>\"off\"</code>. Firefox segue este padrão. Nas&nbsp;versões anteriores do&nbsp;Chrome e&nbsp;IE o padrão é&nbsp;<code>\"inherit\"</code>. No&nbsp;IE6-10, o valor é capitalizado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>designMode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>designMode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"on\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>designMode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"off\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cria um documento&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;editável:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">iframe_node.contentDocument.designMode = \"on\";\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificação","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#making-entire-documents-editable:-the-designmode-idl-attribute\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'designMode' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Feature</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Chrome</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Opera</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Feature</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Android</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">IE Mobile</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th style=\"line-height: 16px;\">Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":" "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also_2","title":"Veja também:","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Rich-Text_Editing_in_Mozilla\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Rich-Text Editing in Mozilla</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/contentEditable\"><code>HTMLElement.contentEditable</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms533720(v=vs.85).aspx\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">designMode property</a> on MSDN</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"especificação"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"&nbsp;","id":"see_also"},{"text":"Veja também:","id":"see_also_2"}],"summary":"document.designMode controla se o documento todo é editável. Valores validos são \"on\" e \"off\". De acordo com a especificação, esta propriedade é por padrão \"off\". Firefox segue este padrão. Nas versões anteriores do Chrome e IE o padrão é \"inherit\". No IE6-10, o valor é capitalizado.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.designMode","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/document/designmode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/fil